<title><anchor id="e-cal-listener-stop-notification"/>e_cal_listener_stop_notification ()</title>
<indexterm><primary>e_cal_listener_stop_notification</primary></indexterm><programlisting><link linkend="void">void</link>        e_cal_listener_stop_notification
                                            (<link linkend="ECalListener">ECalListener</link> *listener);</programlisting>
<para>
Informs a calendar listener that no further notification is desired.  The
callbacks specified when the listener was created will no longer be invoked
after this function is called.</para>
<para>

</para><variablelist role="params">
<varlistentry><term><parameter>listener</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> A calendar listener.
